INSERT INTO `p8_admin_log` (`id`,`uid`,`system`,`module`,`action`,`iid`,`cid`,`site`,`username`,`title`,`url`,`ip`,`data`,`timestamp`) VALUES ('8289','9','cms','item','add','0','1029','','宣传处','添加内容 | “教学案例讨论”的干货若干','/admin.php/cms/item-add','10.10.10.10','array (\n  \'__referer\' => \'http://192.168.162.72/admin.php/cms/item-add?cid=1029&model=article&type=2\',\n  \'cid\' => \'1029\',\n  \'title\' => \'“教学案例讨论”的干货若干\',\n  \'timestamp\' => \'\',\n  \'sub_title\' => \'\',\n  \'author\' => \'\',\n  \'author_x\' => \'\',\n  \'author_y\' => \'\',\n  \'author_z\' => \'\',\n  \'editer\' => \'\',\n  \'source\' => \'教育处\',\n  \'frame\' => \'\',\n  \'thumb_width\' => \'328\',\n  \'thumb_height\' => \'247\',\n  \'summary\' => \'\',\n  \'url\' => \'\',\n  \'views\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_content_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'#field_starttime_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'field#\' => \n  array (\n    \'starttime\' => \'\',\n    \'endtime\' => \'\',\n    \'content\' => \'<p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">在教学查房、小讲课等系列活动中，教学案例讨论无疑是天花板般的存在。看似枯坐的一个小时，无“路径”可寻，却可咸可甜，可高可低，蕴含了大大的智慧，包括欲罢不能的“分层教学”，炙手可热的“翻转课堂”，甚至全民追捧的“混合教学”，都可轻松融入。</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>准备--容易忽略，但非常重要&nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p><p style=\"margin-left: 22px; text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">1、教学病例选择：应以《大纲》或《细则》要求的常见病、多发病为主，可适当&nbsp;选择具有教学价值的少见病例。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left: 22px; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">2、讨论资料准备：应提前发放（非常重要，不能突然讨论）讨论资料，并在资料中明&nbsp;确告知本次病例讨论的中心环节和临床问题，讨论资料&nbsp;可以提前一次性发放，亦可根据教学目的，在教学实施过程&nbsp;中分步呈现。</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3、教学目标/讨论议题的设计：将需要讨论的内容以问题的形式呈现，应明确具体，但不宜过多过广，一般设置 2~3 个目标即可，最多不&nbsp;超过 5 个。</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4、学生准备：学生应提前了解案例，做好资料查阅。</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5、环境准备：（1）影像资料播放设备、白板等。&nbsp;（2）相对安静的示教室，且应布置为适合讨论的围坐模样。</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><img src=\"/attachment/cms/item/2023_10/13_10/411c8c83b1712eb6.jpg.cthumb.jpg\" title=\"图片.jpg\" _src=\"/attachment/cms/item/2023_10/13_10/411c8c83b1712eb6.jpg.cthumb.jpg\" alt=\"图片.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><strong>主体实施--几个容易忽略的要点</strong></p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1、紧紧围绕目标/问题实施：讨论的问题逐级发放，但应紧紧围绕主线实施。</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、勿忘“讨论”的本质，不要演变成小讲课，或者单纯的师生一问一答的简单互动，而是全体学生参与的“讨论”。（因此，提前准备很重要）</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3、将参与者按照能力基础进行单元分割，组成“教学单元”，可实施“分层教学”“翻转课堂”等。</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><strong>总结--小总结，大作用：</strong></p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;讨论结束后，建议实施以下工作：</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1、点评学生表现，板书梳理重点内容；</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、测试学生知识能力获得情况；</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3、布置课后作业并推荐学习材料；</p><p style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-indent: 2em; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 4、教学评估，帮助教师反思提升教学能力。</p><p><br/></p>\',\n  ),\n  \'#field_endtime_posted\' => \'\',\n  \'addon_title\' => \'\',\n  \'list_order\' => \'\',\n  \'verify\' => 1,\n  \'html\' => \'1\',\n  \'html_view_url_rule\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_keywords\' => \'\',\n  \'seo_description\' => \'\',\n  \'custom_a\' => \'\',\n  \'level_time\' => \'权重有效期\',\n  \'level\' => \'\',\n  \'template\' => \'\',\n  \'attachment_pdf\' => \'\',\n  \'config\' => \n  array (\n    \'allow_ip\' => \n    array (\n      \'enabled\' => \'0\',\n      \'collectip\' => \'\',\n      \'area_ip\' => \'\',\n      \'ruleoutip\' => \'\',\n    ),\n  ),\n  \'titl